ce5e7ac6161cdd1c0bbdb56c4d4dcb4d.sql_template:
SELECT 
    m.NomMatiereFr AS nom_matiere,
    n.orale,
    n.TP,
    n.ExamenEcrit,
    n.DS,
    n.DC1,
    n.DC2
FROM 
    noteeleveparmatiere n
JOIN 
    matiere m ON n.id_matiere = m.id
WHERE 
    n.id_inscription IN (SELECT id FROM inscriptioneleve WHERE Eleve IN (SELECT id FROM eleve WHERE IdPersonne IN ({id_personne})));

bd0a735c0b7d88f38cfdc4bcad721b43.sql_template:
SELECT d.LIBELLEDELEGATIONFR AS delegation, COUNT(e.id) AS nombre_eleves
FROM eleve e
JOIN personne p ON e.IdPersonne = p.id
JOIN localite l ON p.Localite = l.IDLOCALITE
JOIN delegation d ON l.CODEDELEGATION = d.id
GROUP BY d.LIBELLEDELEGATIONFR;
